<item>
            <title>[HBASE-43] [hbase] Add a read-only attribute to columns</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-43</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;One day we&apos;ll have support for per-column ACLs.  Meantime, it should be possible to mark loaded content read-only so it doesn&apos;t get trashed accidentally.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12379225">HBASE-43</key>
            <summary>[hbase] Add a read-only attribute to columns</summary>
